en china comen perro y murciélagos, que tengan fetiches de comerse carne de coño a la manera mas literal y bizarra pues es normal... suponiendo que sea normal pensamientos asi.
这是一个架空的虚构世界，和现实一点关系都没有，作者在漫画里描绘了一个庞大的战争时期的世界观，很好的体现出了那种血腥暴力色情的食人和让全裸女兵打仗的行为。秀色世界里面有很森严的等级制度，肉畜为最低级，被作为交易对象，时常还有考核，淘汰下来的人就会被吃掉。我看这个本子的时候一点生理反应都没有，还是思考了很多问题…
Women in the Color world are considered to be 'Gods Food' and consider it a great honor to be eaten. Almost all the meat animals volunteered to be eaten of their own free will.
I don’t get why the females are willing to work for the males who eat them lol
Not gonna lie, this has the be the funniest shit I've seen in a while, can't wait for more to be released

Fucking chinese, sick to the core, misogynist at the heart and ugly in the look. If at least the artwork would have some substance, but it seems like as the author hadn't much time to draw it accoradly, during his 16 hours factory shifts.

Holy shit we got another 7 pages.  Looks like the meat animal is back, and the fight from earlier continues.  Woe be to the soldiers who lose to the meat girl, they'll be taking her place as dinner.  The Battalion Commander is none to happy with this situation.  Not sure what the last 2 pages are, but soon I'll know.
